title: MONDAY 5/10 - ZACH WILSON HITS THE BIG APPLE
itunes:title: MONDAY 5/10 - ZACH WILSON HITS THE BIG APPLE
description:
The Jets held their rookie minicamp (0:11) giving the team its first look at QB Zach Wilson. Head Coach Robert Saleh (0:30) talks about the pressure the rookie QB will be under. Carson Wentz reuniting with Frank Reich in Indianapolis, and Reich (1:17) thinks a fresh start will be good for Wentz. Jalen Hurts replaced went in Philadelphia...GM Howie Roseman (2:39) talks about Hurts' development
